.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, sprite, water
City: boston, berlin, hamburg, new-york
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, mexican, nigerian, polish
 1. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4
 3. the person drinking sprite is not the person traveling to berlin##6
 4. the person drinking water is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 5. the person traveling to boston is the nigerian##1
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is the polish##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the mexican##1
 8. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 9. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the person traveling to new-york and the person drinking sprite##7
10. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up         | sprite    | water  |
| City          | new-york     | berlin | boston | hamburg |
| Nationality   | colombian     | mexican     | nigerian  | polish |

