.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, zombie, romance, animation
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, nigerian, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, bus, taxi
1. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
2. the person watching romance movies is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
4. the american is between the russian and the person watching romance movies##2
5. the person watching romance movies is not the person driving the taxi##6
6. the person watching romance movies is somewhere between the person watching zombie movies and the dutch##7
7. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
9. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4      |
| Movie-Genre         | animation | romance  | zombie  | scientific |
| Nationality   | dutch   | nigerian | american | russian     |
| Transport     | taxi    | bike     | boat     | bus         |

