.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, gospel, jazz, salsa
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, indian, mexican, nigerian
There 4 different types of food: pepper, cabbage, carrot, apple
1. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
2. the indian is the person eating cabbage##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
4. the fan of gospel is the person eating cabbage##1
5. the mexican is the fan of salsa##1
6. the argentine is the person eating pepper##1
7. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
8. the person eating apple is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the fan of jazz##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | blues     | salsa   | jazz      |
| Nationality   | indian    | argentine | mexican | nigerian  |
| Food     | cabbage | pepper  | apple    | carrot |

