The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, d&b, reggae
4 different pets are kept: cat, horse, mouse, rabbit
1. the townhouse house is not the fan of reggae##6
2. the fan of country is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the fan of blues##7
3. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
4. the townhouse house is somewhere between the fan of country and the wooden house##7
5. the wooden house is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the futuristic house is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the mouse is the futuristic house##1
8. the fan of blues is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
| House      | wooden  | townhouse | palace | futuristic |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | d&b  | country  | blues    |
| Pet           | rabbit | cat  | horse    | mouse    |

