1. the egyptian is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
3. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to paris##5
4. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person traveling to paris##1
6. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
7. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to venice##5
8. the person traveling to nizza is not the british##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3      |      4      |
