4. the chef is not the egyptian##6
5. the malaysian is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
6. the brazilian is on the left of the paramedic##1
7. the brazilian is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the project-manager##7
8. the paramedic is not the italian##6
