 3. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the skateboard is between the bolivar-smoker and the davidoff-smoker##2
 5. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the dannemann-smoker##5
 6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 7. the bolivar-smoker is not the person drinking fanta##6
 8. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 9. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the left of the davidoff-smoker##5
10. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
11. the old-henry-smoker is between the davidoff-smoker and the bolivar-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
