 5. the freelancer is somewhere between the person playing whist and the person playing billiard##7
 6. the freelancer is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 7. the scientist is the person watching satire movies##1
 8. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4
 9. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing poker##1
10. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
